title: Gillie & Wallo | Ep 115 | ALL THE SMOKE Full Episode | SHOWTIME Basketball
itunes:title: Gillie & Wallo | Ep 115 | ALL THE SMOKE Full Episode | SHOWTIME Basketball
description:
ATS is back with more big-time guests, as the boys are joined by the hosts of the ‘Million Dollaz Worth of Game' podcast, Wallo and Gillie. The boys dive into the Ben Simmon's saga with the Philadelphia natives and discuss their media journey, including working for Barstool Sports. Plus, they dive into Kyrie & The Nets and the Warriors success.
